<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <title>NordVPN Order Confirmation</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      background-color: #f5f6fa;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      color: #333;
    }
    .container {
      width: 90%;
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      background-color: #fff;
      border-radius: 8px;
      overflow: hidden;
      box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);
      border: 1px solid #d1d5db;
    }
    .header {
      background-color: #1a1a2e;
      color: #fff;
      padding: 20px;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .logo {
      max-height: 50px;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }
    .content {
      padding: 30px;
    }
    .info-block {
      background: #f1f1f1;
      padding: 15px;
      border-radius: 6px;
      margin-top: 15px;
      font-size: 14px;
    }
    .footer {
      padding: 20px;
      text-align: center;
      font-size: 12px;
      color: #999;
    }
    .btn {
      display: inline-block;
      margin-top: 20px;
      padding: 10px 20px;
      background-color: #d85600;
      color: white;
      text-decoration: none;
      border-radius: 4px;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="header">
      <img src="<%= web_url %><%= logo %>" alt="<%= site_name %> Logo" class="logo" />
    </div>

    <div class="content">
      <p>Hello <strong><%= user.full_name %></strong>,</p>

      <p>Thank you for your purchase on <strong><%= site_name %></strong>. Your NordVPN order has been received and is currently being processed.</p>

      <div class="info-block">
        <p><strong>Amount Paid:</strong> <%= currencySymbol %><%= amount %></p>
        <p><strong>Plan:</strong> <%= vpn_plan %></p>
        <p><strong>Status:</strong> Pending Activation</p>
        <p><strong>Order Reference:</strong> <%= reference %></p>
        <p><strong>Date:</strong> <%= date %></p>
      </div>

      <p>Your VPN credentials will be activated shortly. Once the setup is complete, you will receive another email containing your login details and connection information.</p>

      <p>If you have any questions or need assistance, our support team is here to help.</p>

      <a href="<%= web_url %>/support" class="btn">Contact Support</a>

      <p>Thank you for choosing <strong><%= site_name %></strong>.<br>
      We appreciate your trust in us.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="footer">
      &copy; <%= new Date().getFullYear() %> <%= site_name %>. All rights reserved. <br />
      For support, email us at <%= support_email %>.
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
